  05 May 2005; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> portage-2.0.51.21.ebuild:
  Move quickpkg from /usr/bin/ to /usr/sbin/ since only root users can access
  all of / to make proper packages #37271.

*portage-2.0.51-r15 (18 Feb 2005)

  18 Feb 2005; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  portage-2.0.51-r10.ebuild, portage-2.0.51-r11.ebuild,
  portage-2.0.51-r12.ebuild, portage-2.0.51-r13.ebuild,
  portage-2.0.51-r14.ebuild, portage-2.0.51-r15.ebuild,
  portage-2.0.51.16.ebuild:
  Switch to using multilib.eclass rather than querrying profile variables
  directly to fix bug #82027.

